BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260626T110610Z
UID:bwnp-x3ixm04f5wj7-ev-snvjd-20260411110000
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260411T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260411T140000
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a pysanka fundraiser in support of Ukraine and lear
 n the centuries-old Ukrainian art of egg decoration. Attendees will learn 
 the wax-resist technique (using hot wax pen and melting wax over candle) a
 nd enjoy delicious paska (Ukrainian Easter bread) with tea. Your $10 ticke
 t covers all supplies and paska.\nWe encourage attendees to contribute an 
 additional $20 as a donation during the event. Donations will be distribut
 ed among organizations helping those impacted by the ongoing russian invas
 ion of Ukraine (Prytula Foundation\, Sternenko Fund\, and UAnimals)\, prov
 iding military & civilian aid\, medical support\, demining & rebuilding\, 
 and evacuating animals from frontline regions.\n\n\nhttps://bookwhen.com/s
 equoiafabrica/e/ev-snvjd-20260411110000
LOCATION:1736 18th Street\, San Francisco CA 94107-2343
ORGANIZER:mailto:info@sequoiafabrica.org
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Ukrainian Easter Egg (pysanka) Painting 
URL;VALUE=URI:https://bookwhen.com/sequoiafabrica/e/ev-snvjd-20260411110000
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
