BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260626T110610Z
UID:bwnp-x3ixm04f5wj7-ev-s4yfq-20260507183000
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260507T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260507T204500
DESCRIPTION:Gather with us on a drop-in basis for an evening of casual comi
 c drawing! Participants are invited to create a 1-page comic following thi
 s month’s theme: EPIPHANY. All comics will be scanned and shared with at
 tendees as a digital zine.\nAll drawing levels welcome. Bring a pen\, we
 ’ll have paper!\nOBJECTIVES:\n-Bask in spontaneity\n-Meet creatives\n-Su
 rprise yourself\nPanel pals is inspired by the former SF comics meetup Ske
 tchies\, which followed a similar format. Julia and Phoebe were both fans 
 of Sketchies and have missed being able to draw alongside peers…so we ar
 e hoping to bring back that opportunity with Panel Pals!\n\n\nhttps://book
 when.com/sequoiafabrica/e/ev-s4yfq-20260507183000
LOCATION:1736 18th Street\, San Francisco CA 94107-2343
ORGANIZER:mailto:info@sequoiafabrica.org
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Panel Pals!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://bookwhen.com/sequoiafabrica/e/ev-s4yfq-20260507183000
END:VEVENT
