DESCRIPTION:Got a widget you want to model in CAD? Troubleshooting some fea
 tures on a project? Stuck on a tutorial? Have questions on what software t
 o use? Drafting up a drawing for a machine shop?\nCAD office hours are an 
 informal drop-in event\, where we'll try to answer questions and generally
  help out with CAD (2D or 3D) modeling projects. There's no scheduled cont
 ent\, so bring your own project files and tutorials\, and we'll work throu
 gh them together.\n\n\nhttps://bookwhen.com/sequoiafabrica/e/ev-sicw9-2026
 0528180000
LOCATION:1736 18th Street\, San Francisco CA 94107-2343
ORGANIZER:mailto:info@sequoiafabrica.org
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:CAD Office Hours
URL;VALUE=URI:https://bookwhen.com/sequoiafabrica/e/ev-sicw9-20260528180000
END:VEVENT
