BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260626T110611Z
UID:bwnp-x3ixm04f5wj7-ev-szoo1-20260618180000
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260618T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260618T200000
DESCRIPTION:Whether you are an experienced printmaker\, or new to the craft
 \, join us in the workshop for an evening to socialize\, meet other makers
 \, make some messes\, and hopefully some art 🎨🧑‍🎨!\nThis casual
  event will give you the opportunity to flex your creative muscles. We wil
 l have supplies and materials available for experimenting\, and bringing y
 our ideas to life.\nDon't know where to start or what to make? We also hav
 e prefabricated stamps as examples for you to practice printing with.\nThi
 s event is primarily focused on block prints\, which is a type of relief p
 rintmaking (https://ldart.work/printing-relief-techniques-parts-1-to-7/).\
 nThis social often has a waiting list. Please cancel your ticket if you ar
 e not able to attend in order to make room for another student.\n\n\nhttps
 ://bookwhen.com/sequoiafabrica/e/ev-szoo1-20260618180000
LOCATION:1736 18th Street\, San Francisco CA 94107-2343
ORGANIZER:mailto:info@sequoiafabrica.org
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Block Printmaking Social
URL;VALUE=URI:https://bookwhen.com/sequoiafabrica/e/ev-szoo1-20260618180000
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260626T110611Z
UID:bwnp-x3ixm04f5wj7-ev-si9ze-20260625183000
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260625T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260625T213000
DESCRIPTION:Gather with us on a drop-in basis for an evening of casual comi
 c drawing! Participants are invited to create a 1-page comic following thi
 s month’s theme: EPIPHANY. All comics will be scanned and shared with at
 tendees as a digital zine.\nAll drawing levels welcome. Bring a pen\, we
 ’ll have paper!\nOBJECTIVES:\n-Bask in spontaneity\n-Meet creatives\n-Su
 rprise yourself\nPanel pals is inspired by the former SF comics meetup Ske
 tchies\, which followed a similar format. Julia and Phoebe were both fans 
 of Sketchies and have missed being able to draw alongside peers…so we ar
 e hoping to bring back that opportunity with Panel Pals!\n\n\nhttps://book
 when.com/sequoiafabrica/e/ev-si9ze-20260625183000
LOCATION:1736 18th Street\, San Francisco CA 94107-2343
ORGANIZER:mailto:info@sequoiafabrica.org
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Panel Pals!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://bookwhen.com/sequoiafabrica/e/ev-si9ze-20260625183000
END:VEVENT
