 ost\, Cheryl\, is a long time crocheter (mostly amigurumi) but has recentl
 y learned some basic knitting\, so if you’re interested in learning eith
 er she can help. Bring a project\, socialize\, and get to know our space! 
 \n\n\nhttps://bookwhen.com/sequoiafabrica/e/ev-szib6-20260723190000
